snippet.title: Final Profit: A Shop RPG - Gameplay Trailer August 2022
snippet.description:
https://www.finalprofit.com.au/

Final Profit is a merchant life-sim RPG & parody of capitalism.

Manage your shop, make investments, and explore a story filled world as you work to earn enough coin to take down the corrupt Bureau of Business! 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1705140/Final_Profit_A_Shop_RPG/

Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/FinalProfitRPG
Follow on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@finalprofitrpg
Join the Discord: https://discord.com/invite/VX7M58RfJn
Like on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/finalprofit
